# Vue 3 E-commerce Rules
- Stack: Vue 3 (Composition API), Vite, Tailwind CSS, shadcn-vue.
- State: Use Pinia for the shopping cart (store/cart.ts).
- Components: Use Single File Components (.vue) with <script setup lang="ts">.
- Styling: Use Tailwind CSS and Lucide Vue icons.
- Formatting: Prefer PascalCase for component filenames and kebab-case in templates.
- Behavior:
  - Do not use the Options API (no 'data()', 'methods', etc.).
  - Always use TypeScript for props and emits definitions.
  - Automatically suggest shadcn-vue components when building UI.